Privacy Policy for Sparky

Last Updated: 25-2-2025

Introduction:
Sparky is an AI-powered search application that respects and protects user privacy. This policy explains how we handle your data.

Information Collection and Use:
1. User Account Information:
- We only collect basic account information (email) necessary for authentication
- Passwords are securely encrypted and stored
- No personal identification information is required

2. Search Data:
- Search queries are processed in real-time
- Queries are not permanently stored
- Search history remains on your device only

3. App Permissions:
- We only request essential permissions required for app functionality
- No access to contacts, location, or other sensitive data

Data Security:
- All data transmission is encrypted using industry-standard protocols
- We implement secure cloud infrastructure
- Regular security audits are performed

Data Sharing:
- We do not sell user data
- We do not share personal information with third parties
- No advertising networks are used

User Rights:
- You can request account deletion at any time
- You can export your data
- You control what information you share

Children's Privacy:
Our service is not directed to children under 13 years of age.

Updates to Privacy Policy:
We may update this privacy policy occasionally. Users will be notified of any significant changes.

Contact Us:
For any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:
qubiqstudio@gmail.com

By using Sparky, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
